source:
TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
The intrepid miner has his eye on the disused facilities of Malikah's Well.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Cet ouvrier motivé a besoin d'aide pour inspecter le dispositif de pompage du Puits de Makilah.
TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_TODO_01<tab>Faire votre rapport à l'ouvrier motivé

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_000<tab>I've seen you before. Part of the group that went into Malikah's Well, right?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_000<tab>Tiens, mais j'te r'connais<var 1D /var>! Tu fais partie du groupe qui s'est battu au Puits de Malikah, non<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_001<tab>Thought so. Thanks to you lot getting rid of the sin eaters around here, there's a chance we might be able to put these remnants of Nabaath Areng to good use.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_001<tab>Je l'savais<var 1D /var>! Grâce à votre victoire sur l'grand purgateur, la recon<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion du puits s'met en place p'tit à p'tit<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_002<tab>The well was originally dug under the orders of some malikah or the other, I forget which. She used cool water from underground to keep off the desert heat.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_002<tab>Dans l'temps, cet endroit était un p'tit bassin utilisé pour profiter de l'eau sous-terraine bien fraîche<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_003<tab>Years later, when the mining industry hit its stride, the need for water in the ore washing process led to its expansion. But as you can tell, it's been in a state of disrepair for years now.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_003<tab>Avec l'expansion de l'industrie minière, on a commencé à avoir besoin d'l'eau en plus grande quantité pour l'lavage des minéraux, et l'puits a peu à peu été agrandi jusqu'à atteindre sa taille actuelle.

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_004<tab>Still, we'd be fools to let the well go to waste, so I'm looking into getting the old machinery working again. Some of it's a bit tricky to get to, though, and I could do with a hand. So, fancy earning a few gil?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_004<tab>Avant d'commencer la reconstuction, j'voudrais vérifier l'état du dispositif de pompage, tu serais d'accord pour m'aider<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_005<tab>I need you to inspect the lift for carrying workers and the giant pulley for drawing up water. I'd like to know if they can still be used or if they're rusted to buggery.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_005<tab>J'm'occupe de l'équipement au sol, tu peux aller voir dans quel état est l'matériel en haut<var 1D /var>? J'échangerais bien, mais j'ai l'vertige... Il faudra que tu trouves un moyen sûr de grimper là-haut, par contre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_010<tab>What's the matter? Not scared of heights are you?
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_010<tab>J'm'occupe de l'équipement au sol, tu peux aller voir dans quel état est l'matériel en haut<var 1D /var>? Fais attention à pas tomber<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>Although some of the less important parts are in need of replacement, the mechanism itself appears to be in good condition.

TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_030<tab>Hmm... It sounds like it won't take much to have them in working order. When I share the good news with the folk in Twine, I'm sure they'll send a few laborers to help with the repairs.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_030<tab>Juste un peu d'rouille tu dis<var 1D /var>? Hum, avec un peu de réparation, ça devrait refonctionner<var 1D /var>! Quand les autres entendront ça, ils accepteront sûrement d'm'aider<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_031<tab>Getting Malikah's Well producing water again will be a good start, but we'll need the Talos up and running to have any chance of reviving the mining industry in these parts.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_031<tab>Imagine un peu<var 1D /var>! Grâce à la réactivation des talos et la restauration du puits, la région redeviendra bien vite l'immense ex<var 16 /var>ploi<var 16 /var>ta<var 16 /var>tion minière d'autrefois<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_032<tab>We'd best take it one step at a time, though. And you helping me here was one such step. Your reward, as promised.
target: TEXT_LUCKZH203_03531_MINER03531_000_032<tab>J'ai hâte d'voir ce jour arriver<var 1D /var>! Tu m'as bien aidé, voyage<var 08 E905 ((use)) ((ur)) /var>, merci<var 1D /var>!
